"{\"uid\": \"morningstaronline.co.uk-article-eurostar-staff-suspend-industrial-ballot-after-securing-olympics-bonus\", \"text\": \"TRANSPORT union RMT\\u00a0secured improved payments for Eurostar staff working the Olympic games following intense negotiations and a ballot for industrial action.  Eurostar had initially proposed a shift-based payment system, which RMT rejected as divisive and insufficient.  The rail company has now agreed to provide a one-off bonus instead, averting the threat of industrial action during what is expected to be a busy period.\"}"